# =============================================================================
# Platform Core – Environment (Foundation Stack)
# =============================================================================
# Runtime env nam trong: ai_content_director/.env (copy tu ai_content_director/.env.example).
#
# Cho Docker Compose (tu repo root):
#   - POSTGRES_PASSWORD: mat khau Postgres (mac dinh: postgres).
#   - N8N_HOST, N8N_WEBHOOK_URL: cho n8n (prod: set domain va https).
#   - Cac bien khac cho API: dat trong ai_content_director/.env.
#
# SECRETS – Khong commit gia that vao git:
#   - POSTGRES_PASSWORD (prod: manh, khac dev)
#   - OPENAI_API_KEY (ai_content_director/.env)
#   - FACEBOOK_ACCESS_TOKEN, FACEBOOK_PAGE_ID (ai_content_director/.env)
#   - N8N encryption key (neu dung N8N_ENCRYPTION_KEY)
# Luon dung .env (da them vao .gitignore) va doc tu env khi chay container.
# =============================================================================
